This paper deals with the topic of cryptography and neural networks, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also involves training neural networks adversarially, which is a common technique in machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper involves the use of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE) to achieve its goals. Finally, the paper deals with the topic of confidentiality in communication systems, which could fall under the category of social and information networks (cs.SI).
